struments, and assuming the VHE gamma-ray emission to\nbe produced by the inverse Compton mechanism, the magnetic field strength can\nbe directly estimated to be of the order of 1 G.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Jun 2005 19:04:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Jun 2005 14:47:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
